Class InputKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • Green.InputKey

  • public class InputKey
extends java.lang.Object
    A class for storing a key input for (primarily-internal) use. It stores both the char key and the int keyCode of the input.
    Author:
    Zacchary Dempsey-Plante
